title: PHOTOS: Emily Ratajkowski Shares Completely Nude Snap While On Vacation
text:
TOP 5541154 
Emily Ratajkowski shared a completely nude photograph from her vacation in Mexico on Instagram Sunday with her 11.8 million followers. 
The 25-year-old Sports Illustrated Swimsuit model was captured in the buff while lying under the sun in a pool of water surrounded by rocks. (RELATED: Emily Ratajkowski Just Showed A Jaw-Dropping Amount Of Sideboob In This Photo) Picture by: Splash News/DKNY 
In the caption next to the post she wrote, “La Sirena,” which according to google translate means The Mermaid. (RELATED: Emily Ratajkowski’s Swimsuit Can’t Contain Her Cleavage…AT ALL) 
A post shared by Emily Ratajkowski (@emrata) on Mar 19, 2017 at 1:11pm PDT 
In a post she shared on Saturday, she shared a photo wearing an army green bikini that fit her perfectly and showed off a ton of cleavage. She captioned the post, “Morning” and included a Mexico flag emoji. 
A post shared by Emily Ratajkowski (@emrata) on Mar 19, 2017 at 7:59am PDT
